arts.ttl: Champions League Qualifier Preview: Shelbourne -v- Linfield
arts.sum: League of Ireland champions Shelbourne take on Northern Irish Premiership kingpins Linfield in the first-leg of their Champions League first qualifying round tie at Tolka Park on Wednesday night (kick-off is at 7.45pm). Shels will have a fully fit squad going into the tie but will be without the suspended Sean Gannon for the first leg after he was sent off in a win away to Gibraltarians St Joseph's last year.
